          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This delegate method only applies to column-style split view interfaces. For more information, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uisplitviewcontroller#3596562"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The split view controller calls this method when one of its columns is about to be hidden, for example with "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uisplitviewcontroller/3580903-hidecolumn"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Use this method to perform any customization associated with hiding the column. You can use the split view controller’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiviewcontroller/1619294-transitioncoordinator"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to coordinate any of your animations alongside the transition animation."
            }
          ]
        },
